Roger L. Jackson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_L._Jackson 0 Roger Labon Jackson (born July 13, 1958) is an American voice actor. He is best known for voicing Ghostface in the Scream film series, where E! ranked him as #46 on Best Kept Secrets of Hollywood. He is also well known for voicing the character Mojo Jojo on The Powerpuff Girls and its 2016 reboot. Roger_Labon_Jackson ( born July_13_,_1958 ) is an_American_voice_actor .
